      "content": "The function is $g(x)=3x$. If $g(x)=12$, then $$3x=12$$"
    },
    {
      "title": "Solve for x",
      "content": "Divide both sides by $3$: $$x=4$$"
    },
    {
      "title": "Answer",
      "content": "The value of $x$ is <strong>4</strong>."
    },
    {
      "title": "Verify by substitution",
      "content": "Substitute $x=4$ back into the function: $g(4)=3(4)=12$. That matches the required output, so the free-response answer is <strong>4</strong>."
